blog.name: blurrydawgo
blog.title: Blurry's now ran off to Twitter/DA
blog.description: (18, American-British, "he/him", currently on indefinite and possibly permanent hiatus, also on Instagram/DA/Twitter/Pillowfort under the same "BlurryDawgo" username) Hi, call me Blurry! I'm a small-time artist and science fanatic with autism. My interests mostly include Sonic, Sly Cooper, and a lot of other stuff in-between. Here's where I post some art, some thoughts, some sociopolitical stuff, the occassional signal boost, etc. (As of recently, any posts with heavy stressful/problematic content will be tagged with "blurrydiscourse", so if you wanna follow me but don't want your dash filled with sociopoliti-crap, filter that out.) If you want to talk to me, just hit that askbox. Don't be shy.
